	Hakibuscon picks up heavy fire on a Maximal base(correct me if I'm wrong
I'm just trying to get Hakibuscon's act together).  He did not care if it

wanted a place in the war.  He sped to the base as quick as he could,
hoping to get there in time to try and save the base.
